title: PV Calc v1.0 android
description:
Requirements: 2.3.3+

Overview: The PV Calculator is an all in one tool for use by both individuals and installers of Solar PV Systems.

This calculator helps you to calculate
- The required Solar Panels required for your domestic use
- The battery bank capacity required for the installation.
As an Installer it helps you to determine
- The Losses in your proposed installation
- The required cable size
- The Size of Charge Controller to be used
- The Ratings of your protective devices

This app has no advertisements.
